{"lemma":"غَلْبَةٌ","slug":"غَلْبَةٌ","root":"غ.ل.ب","root_slug":"غ-ل-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ل-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32190","n32197","n32198","n32199"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَلَبَ (ḡalaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"triumph, victory"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَلَبَ (ḡalaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَلَبَ (ḡalaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of غَالِب (ḡālib)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣa.la.ba/","/ɣu.lub.ba/","/ɣa.lub.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32190","headword_ar":"غَلَبَهُ","root":"glb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galaba Ealayohi","text_ar":"غَلَبَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabN","text_ar":"غَلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galobN","text_ar":"غَلْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) the former of which is the more chaste, (TA,) or the latter is an inf. n. and the former is a simple subst., (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabapN","text_ar":"غَلَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) [the most common form,] or this is a simple subst. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabN","text_ar":"غَلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) which is perhaps formed from it by the elision of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magolabN","text_ar":"مَغْلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magolabapN","text_ar":"مَغْلَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) which last is rare, (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galaAbiyapN","text_ar":"غَلَابِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [in an intensive sense]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gulub~aY","text_ar":"غُلُبَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilib~aY","text_ar":"غِلِبَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gulub~apN","text_ar":"غُلُبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, K, TA, said in the S to be syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabapN","text_ar":"غَلَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galub~apN","text_ar":"غَلُبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"g","text_ar":"غ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"glab~ap","text_ar":"غلَبَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilib~aA='u","text_ar":"غِلِبَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kr, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, overcame, conquered, subdued, overpowered, mastered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surpassed, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it; gained ascendency"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the mastery, prevailed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"predominated, over him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, superior in power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"influence, to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, MA, K, PS, TK, &c.) [See also 5.] ―         -b2-  One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabotuhu Ealayohi","text_ar":"غَلَبْتُهُ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I overcame him in contending for it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I took it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obtained it, from him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by superior power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guliba fulaAnN EalaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"غُلِبَ فُلَانٌ عَلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one had the thing taken from him by superior power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tugolabuwA EalaY SalaApK","text_ar":"لَا تُغْلَبُوا عَلَى صَلَاةٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabola TuluwEi Al$~amosi waqabola guruwbihaA","text_ar":"قَبْلَ طُلُوعِ الشَّمْسِ وَقَبْلَ غُرُوبِهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be not ye overcome and anticipated"},{"kind":"text","text":"by others"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in performing prayer before the rising of the sun and before its setting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"so that the opportunity for your doing so escape you. (Mgh.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabahu EalaY nafosihi","text_ar":"غَلَبَهُ عَلَى نَفْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He forced him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constrained him against his will."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b4-  [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabahu AlA^amoru","text_ar":"غَلَبَهُ الاَمْرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The affair overcame, defeated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baffled, him."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabahu biAlxawofi","text_ar":"غَلَبَهُ بِالخَوْفِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exceeded him in fear."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xwf","text_ar":"خوف"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galaba EalaY fulaAnK Alkaramu","text_ar":"غَلَبَ عَلَى فُلَانٍ الكَرَمُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Generosity was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, the predominant quality of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galaba A^ano yuxoTama","text_ar":"غَلَبَ اَنْ يُخْطَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He refused to have the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiTaAm","text_ar":"خِطَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leading-rope"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put upon him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; said of a camel. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xTm","text_ar":"خطم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayugolabu A^aHadukumo","text_ar":"اَيُغْلَبُ اَحَدُكُمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano yuSaAHiba Aln~aAsa maEoruwfFA","text_ar":"اَنْ يُصَاحِبَ النَّاسَ مَعْرُوفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayaEojizu","text_ar":"اَيَعْجِزُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Is any one of you unable to associate with men kindly?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galiba","text_ar":"غَلِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galabN","text_ar":"غَلَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, thick-necked:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thick and short in the neck:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thick"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2280},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and inclining in the neck:"},{"kind":"text","text":"from disease or other cause. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","Fr","Kr"]},{"entry_id":"n32197","headword_ar":"غَلَبَةٌ","root":"glb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galaba","text_ar":"غَلَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA,) or a simple subst. (Msb.) [It is much used as a subst., signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of overcoming, conquering, subduing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; (see 1;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"victory, conquest, ascendency, mastery, prevalence, predominance, superiority."},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"superior power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"influence; success in a contest;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of taking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obtaining, by superior power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force."},{"kind":"text","text":"]       -A2-  And pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAlibN","text_ar":"غَالِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n32198","headword_ar":"غُلَبَةٌ","root":"glb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n32199","headword_ar":"غُلُبَّةٌ","root":"glb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galub~apN","text_ar":"غَلُبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galab~apN","text_ar":"غَلَبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%BA%D9%84%D8%A8%D8%A9/","headword_ar":"غلبة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_15","lexicon_en":"Ibn Mālik, al-Alfāẓ al-Mukhtalifa fī l-Maʿānī al-Muʾtalifa (d. 1274 CE)","lexicon_ar":"الألفاظ المختلفة في المعاني المؤتلفة لابن مالك","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=22395#310166","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">بَاب الْغَلَبَة</span><br><br><span>أجبرته وأكرهته وقسرته وغلبته وقهرته عنْوَة صاغرا</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_15","lexicon_en":"Ibn Mālik, al-Alfāẓ al-Mukhtalifa fī l-Maʿānī al-Muʾtalifa (d. 1274 CE)","lexicon_ar":"الألفاظ المختلفة في المعاني المؤتلفة لابن مالك","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=22395#c3cc67","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">بَاب الْغَلَبَة</span><br><br><span>إستيلاؤه واحتواؤه وغلبته واشتماله واعتلاؤه والتحافه واستحواذه واعتراؤه واحتياره</span>"}]}}